ation can be as cheap as reading the data twice from main memory. As a\nconsequence, an implementation that achieves realistic performance will move\nthe limit at which one has to resort to randomized methods that only process\npart of the data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 22:56:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Oct 2021 19:38:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 12:55:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
